citations:
    citation-adwd-theon:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Theon"
            text_from_source: "Theon grabbed Jeyne about the waist and jumped."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Theon POV (chapter titled 'Theon', the first to use his real name). Little Walder's body found — Big Walder discovered it. Hosteen Frey accuses Manderly. Manderly knights wound Hosteen. Bolton sends Freys and Manderlys out through separate gates to fight Stannis. Abel's spearwives — Rowan, Squirrel, Holly, Frenya, Willow Witch-Eye, Myrtle — escort Theon to rescue 'Arya' (Jeyne Poole). They get Jeyne out of her room disguised as Squirrel. At the Battlements Gate: Holly kills one guard; Frenya kills the other. Holly killed by crossbow bolt. Frenya stays behind to hold pursuers. Theon jumps from the battlements with Jeyne."
